    <item>
      <title>美国服务业增长放缓，支付价格创四年新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/us-services-growth-eases-prices-paid-hit-four-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3 月份美国服务业增长连续第二个月放缓，而材料和服务支付价格指数下降超过 5 个百分点，至 2020 年 3 月以来的最低水平。迈克尔·麦基 (Michael McKee) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上了解了详细信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/us-services-growth-eases-prices-paid-hit-four-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:24:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多承诺再提供数十亿美元的公寓建设贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，即将出台的联邦预算将在公寓建设贷款计划中再投入 150 亿加元（合 111 亿美元），这是他为解决加拿大人口激增导致的住房短缺问题所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着需求飙升，乐天将垃圾债券发售规模增至 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/rakuten-boosts-junk-bond-sale-to-2-billion-as-demand-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鉴于投资者的强劲需求，乐天集团 (Rakuten Group Inc.) 将其美国高收益债券发行规模扩大至 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/rakuten-boosts-junk-bond-sale-to-2-billion-as-demand-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
